[thinking] I’m noticing a subtlety with `DefaultStyledDocument` attributes, specifically around open and close after `document.insertString`. It seems that there might be a situation where the bold attribute is set to false when working with a highlighter. It’s interesting to think through how these attributes can affect the final display of the text. I want to make sure I understand this clearly, so I’ll keep pondering the implications on the styling and functionality.
